		TNT1 A 0 A_JumpIfInventory("RevolverAlt",1,"StopAlt")
		DARN ABCDE 1
		Goto ActualFanningFire
	ActualFanningFire:
		DARN F 2
		DARN GH 1
		Goto FanningAmmoCheck
